g experience for users of all skill levels, with a team of skilled musicians and AI experts behind its development.', NULL, '["AI Tools","Art Generation","Content Creation"]');
INSERT INTO products (id,created_at,name,url,website_image_url,icon_url,meta,description,category_id,subcategory) VALUES ('6855b89d-45bd-4513-960e-2349d7c83dab', '2024-04-12T15:29:31.611Z', 'Supa Doc', 'https://www.supadoc.ai/', 'images/supa-doc.webp', 'images/supa-doc-icon.webp', '{"what":"Supa Doc is a software as a service (SaaS) product for system engineers that leverages machine learning, specifically GPT4, to automate the creation of various types of documents.","who":"Supa Doc is designed for system engineers, developers, product managers, marketing managers, entrepreneurs, and software testers who need to create detailed and high-quality documents efficiently.","best_features":["Automated document creation using GPT4 machine learning technology","Support for multiple document types including Marketing Plans, Software System Specifications, and Business Plans","Low code agility and AI Native Engine for streamlined document generation"],"pricing":[{"plan":"Monthly subscription","price":49.99,"billing_cycle":"per month","original_price":59.99,"discount":"17% off","features":["Unlimited AI document creations","Premium customer support","Future updates including AI translations and automated marketing copywriting"]},{"plan":"Pay-as-you-go","price":0.25,"billing_cycle":"per document","original_price":0.3,"discount":"17% off","features":["Flexible usage based on needs","Upgrade or downgrade plans easily","Secure data protection protocols"]}]}', 'Supa Doc is a SaaS product that automates document creation using GPT4 machine learning technology. It supports various document types, multiple languages, and offers low code agility for efficient content generation. With pricing plans catering to different usage needs and advanced data protection protocols, Supa Doc aims to simplify and enhance the document creation process for professionals.', NULL, '["Document Generation","AI Writing","Productivity Tools"]');
