lture by leveraging individual differences. With continuous machine learning adaptation, Team Assessment evolves with the team, providing tailored advice and guidance. It is ideal for organisations seeking to enhance collaboration, productivity, and team dynamics.', NULL, '["AI Solutions","Team Building","Workplace Culture"]');
